    - target: {fileID: 5992790046328815897, guid: e7301deb731adf14eae8e8bf154c6710, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '11 cards are dealt to you at the start. Arrange them to form valid
        groups.

        Each turn: draw a card from the deck or discard pile, then
        discard one card.

        Win: reach a score of 10 or less after discarding
        your worst card.

        Timer: 30 seconds per turn. On timeout, a card
        is auto-drawn and the worst card is discarded.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
